	 	 	 	 HEADLINE 
Radhika Apte Didn't Even Care Them
	 	 	 	 CONTENT 
Like many of the celebrities who had faced social media trolls and dealt with them with dignity, Radhika Apte too knew how to deal with haters in quite a composed manner. Recently, she was trolled for sporting a bikini on Goa’s beach when she went for a holiday.

When asked how she felt about being trolled and how does she deal with them, Radhika says she doesn’t need to deal with them as she doesn’t know them. Coming to body shaming on her bikini dress, Radhika asked the trolls if they expect her to wear a sari on a beach.

While we know that she is sensible to ignore the trolls, it has become quite an impossible task to keep a check on faceless and jobless trolls who keep waiting to find an unnecessary issue to turn into a big controversial point.

